bodyShape.name: Rectangle
bodyShape.description: A rectangular body shape is characterized by a relatively balanced proportion between the bust, waist, and hips. The waist is not significantly defined, and there is minimal curve between the waist and hips, resulting in a more straight-up-and-down figure.
